# gnBlogPlugin

## Security

Administration security (gnBlogPageAdmin) is **on** by default and requires the
permission 'admin_blog'. This permission can be customized by setting in the
app.yml the 'gn_wiki_admin_credential' property. This permission is added to the
'admin' group from the gnCorePlugin fixtures file.

Visitor security (gnBlogPage) is **off** by default. It can be enabled by setting
in the app.yml the 'gn_blog_is_private' property to true. By default permission
is 'visitor_blog'. This permission can be customized by setting in the
app.yml the 'gn_blog_visitor_credential' property.

